description: Happy Valentine's Day! Today's guest, Dawoon Kang, is the CEO of Coffee Meets Bagel, a dating app for real relationships. She will speak about some of the pitfalls we fall into with dating apps and what things we can do to set us up for success. We will also talk about knowing what you are looking for and the best way to present that.
